'ML TO DATA' CONVERTS DATA IN MEMORYTO APPLESOFT DATA STATEMENTS.  INRESPONSE TO THE PROMPT; ENTER THESTARTING       ADDRESS (IN DECIMAL);THE ENDING        ADDRESS; THESTARTING APPLESOFT LINENUMBER; THE LINE NUMBER INCREMENT(E.G.;10); AND THE FILENAME TO STORETHE      'DATA' STATEMENTS IN.AFTER THE NEW FILE IS CREATED;'EXEC' ITTO ADD THE NEW LINES TO THEAPPLESOFT   PROGRAM IN MEMORY.